Deploy Wazuh SIEM in AWS for Log Collection and Alerting
Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Deploy Wazuh SIEM platform on AWS using infrastructure as code
Configure Wazuh to collect and process AWS security logs
Implement Python automation for log analysis and alert generation
Create custom rules and decoders for threat detection
Generate security intelligence reports from collected logs
Prerequisites
Students should have:

Basic Linux command line knowledge
Understanding of AWS services (EC2, VPC, CloudTrail)
Python programming fundamentals
Familiarity with SIEM concepts and log analysis
Lab Environment
Al Nafi provides pre-configured cloud machines with all necessary tools:

